\begin_layout Plain Layout

[Inviscid Burgers Equation]
\end_layout

\end_inset

If 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 is proportional to 
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

, i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $a(u)=ku$
\end_inset

, then PDE
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:QuasilinearWaveEquation"
